01:02:20,980 --> 01:02:24,980
Like LP little A. Well, we were starting to learn how to lower up. That's another topic, I guess.

506
01:02:24,980 --> 01:02:26,980
We're not going to get to LP little A today.

507
01:02:26,980 --> 01:02:32,980
That's another topic. But yes, it's a genetic factor that is associated with risk that we don't yet know what to do with.

