01:20:24,980 --> 01:20:28,980
We just talked earlier about the European Consensus Group that I was on.

692
01:20:28,980 --> 01:20:31,980
Well, there was a second one that I was on, and it was...

693
01:20:31,980 --> 01:20:32,980
Statin side effects.

